org.eclipse.papyrus.MARTE.MARTE_DesignModel.HRM.HwLogical.HwStorage.HwStorageManager

Interface HwMMU

  • All Superinterfaces:
    org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, HwResource, HwStorageManager, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier, Resource, StorageResource
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    HwMMUImpl

    public interface HwMMU
extends HwStorageManager
    A representation of the model object 'Hw MMU'.

    The following features are supported:

    • Virtual Addr Space
    • Physical Addr Space
    • Memory Protection
    • Nb Entries
    • Owned TL Bs
    See Also:
    HwStorageManagerPackage.getHwMMU()
